FireStrike looked to his supposed called brother.  "You will never 
talk for me again, brother. If I want orders I will ask for them. I 
am tired of your exhaust sucking to Megatron.  Now either respect em 
and yourself, or feel my rage." FireStrike said as he from out of 
subspaace he pulled his gigantic sword.  He had never felt like this 
before.  After the shot from Megatron he had lost his programming to 
always be controlled by someone else. He was finally his own bot. And 
he was pissed.
